Egg group - AMORPHOUS / MINERAL

The true form of this {POKEMON} is unknown. Beneath the bandages, it molds its rocky body into an effigy of its adversary.
The hard shell beneath the bandages contains a turbulent air sac. This {POKEMON} has expert control over the air flow. A controlled release produces high winds or earsplitting groans.
